  "contents": "<div class=\"content markitup-box\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t有道是：<br/>\n<b>祖国噘起蹲着弄</b><br/>\n<b>汉唐盛世早练过</b><br/>\n<b>民族恶臭共享受</b><br/>\n<b>社交恐惧坑中没。</b><br/>\n<br/>\n<b>《中国大陆热爱蹲坑茅厕门户大敞互相观摩闻味交流欣赏之原因</b>》<br/>\r\n1。简单方便不必冲洗完事提裤抬腿消失<br/>\r\n2。无下水道堵塞泛滥开门关门上锁之忧<br/>\r\n3。人多热闹笑语喧声互动频繁减低抑郁<br/>\r\n4。空气流通味道横窜锻炼呼吸道喉头肌<br/>\r\n5。爱国监控警惕防谍抑制不良情绪泄露<br/>\r\n6。节省材料有效增加每平方米排泄效率<br/>\r\n7。怀旧感恩回望汉唐盛世体验祖国强大<br/>\r\n8。提升民族自豪感全自主产权炎黄风味<br/>\r\n9。增强腿部肌肉平衡力量准备攻打台湾。<br/>\n<br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly9pLmltZ3VyLmNvbS95VDlHMmR5LmpwZWc\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://i.imgur.com/yT9G2dy.jpeg\"><img alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/yT9G2dy.jpeg\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/yT9G2dy.jpeg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly9pLmltZ3VyLmNvbS92WGEzdWNwLmpwZWc\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://i.imgur.com/vXa3ucp.jpeg\"><img alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/vXa3ucp.jpeg\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/vXa3ucp.jpeg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\n<br/>\n<a href=\"https://pincong.rocks/article/38242\" title=\"https://pincong.rocks/article/38242\"><b>乱世笑林</b></a> </div>",
